snippet.title: MISTER MIXMANIA
snippet.description:
MISTER MIXMANIA is a FREE  Promotion and Support Provider for artists from the genres deep house, dance music, electronic, chill out, nu disco, indie dance and funky house. We support and promote talented artists from many areas (musicians / labels, composers, producers, photographers / filmmakers) ASK US

Send your song, video or pictures on Mister Mixmania: https://submission.mister-mixmania.com

 - Thank you for your trust.

ENJOY THE SOUND OF MUSIC
------------------------★----------------------
